ut this. Hence, more\nmeasurements of the proper motions at high R and |z| are necessary to validate\nthe exotic scenario that would arise if this low speed were confirmed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2014 19:01:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Feb 2014 14:43:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
