 with cloud\ntracking observations of Jupiter and Saturn.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 15 Feb 2014 12:04:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Mar 2014 11:08:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
